headline: Owner at THE ICE GROUP
summary:
THE ICE GROUP:  

Providing Process Services for attorneys and law firms nation wide, Notary, Custody and Property Exchange supervision, Discreet Inquires, Immigration and Customs consulting.  Backed by 36 years of combined military (4 years) and federal criminal investigative (32 years) experience. French and Spanish languages.   Specializing in skip tracing and others who attempt to avoid being served.
